{"type":"article","id":10990,"title":"台灣 YouTuber 拒絕刪除與蔡英文合拍之短片而被列為台獨份子、微博密碼遭橄欖","uid":6868,"topics":[229,275,673,1134],"contents":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PKpotterking/posts/2563680140532662\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PKpotterking/posts/2563680140532662</a><br>\n<br>\n昨天才剛解鎖人生成就，今天就有突發狀況。<br>\n.<br>\n以下是我們中國新媒體合作方的訊息，之前其實就有跟他們說過不要干涉我們的創作內容<br>\n了。<br>\n<br>\n.<br>\n而今天他們不只干涉還過頭了<br>\n他們的重點放在「總統」兩個字都不能出現，看到這裡我跟Mars他們討論後完全沒辦法接<br>\n受，真的太扯了。<br>\n<br>\n.<br>\n然後我微博大概一百多萬人<br>\n帳號都是我們自己經營的，直接被他們改密碼端走，現在登入不進去了。<br>\n.<br>\n如果要我們不能稱呼自己國家的元首為「總統」那這筆錢我們不賺也罷....<br>\n.<br>\n這每個月損失雖然不小，但我們真的跪不下去。<br>\n<br>\n#很多台灣人覺得民主很正常<br>\n#實際上民主真他媽可貴<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/MsAqacm.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MsAqacm.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/MsAqacm.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/44I3IGJ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/44I3IGJ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/44I3IGJ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/4WWdLde.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4WWdLde.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/4WWdLde.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/C9ahTbI.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/C9ahTbI.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/C9ahTbI.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/V9H1oiC.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/V9H1oiC.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/V9H1oiC.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-15","agreeCount":60,"discussionCount":0}